      Data: 75|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: "Total GPU mesh decode budget per frame in milliseconds (aggregate across
        all chunks). The proven path is mesh-bound on the readback->CPU-decode while
        data-gen sits at ~0% during load, leaving this budget's frame-share unused
        \u2014 so it is set generously to spend the idle CPU on draining mesh decodes.
        The adaptive system shrinks it if frames get heavy."
    - Name: 
