      Data: 216|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: 'Experimental (default OFF): extract many chunks'' faces in ONE blit
        over a tiled RT + ONE region readback, then demux on the CPU. Cuts the per-chunk
        readback request/callback count by the batch tile count. Falls back to the
        per-chunk path for interaction/resident chunks. Off = unchanged per-chunk
        path.'
