      Data: 225|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: 'GPU-resident #2 STEP 2 (default OFF): skip the GPU->CPU column readback
        at gen-time for chunks that don''t need a CPU mirror. Their blocks live only
        in the atlas (repacked GPU->GPU from the column final texture) and rehydrate
        on demand. Requires enableGpuResidentChunks. This is what actually eliminates
        the data-gen readback latency.'
